Class PatternEncoder

java.lang.Object
io.jstach.rainbowgum.pattern.format.PatternEncoder
All Implemented Interfaces:
LogEncoder
public final class PatternEncoder extends Object implements LogEncoder
Factory for pattern encoders.
API Note
This class is for API discoverability. Pattern Encoders do not actually extend or implement this class.
